description:
Certain makeup colors can reduce redness on your cheeks and other areas of your face. Learn about makeup colors that reduce redness with help from a celebrity makeup artist in this free video clip.

Expert: Jhizet Panosian
Bio: Jhizet Panosian is a celebrity makeup artist.
Filmmaker: Richard Benton

Series Description: When selecting makeup for a night out or even just a regular day it is always important to keep a few things in mind. Learn all about makeup selection and application with help from a celebrity makeup artist in this free video series.
title: Makeup Colors That Reduce Redness
